### Admin Login
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "admin123456"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.token);
%}

### ----------------------------------------
### Reseller Register
POST http://localhost:8080/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "phone": "0812345678",
  "password": "password123",
  "confirmPassword": "password123",
  "shopName": "Jane Shop",
  "address": "123 Bangkok"
}

### ----------------------------------------
### Admin Get Resellers to Approve (Find ID of Jane Doe)
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/resellers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------
### Admin Approves Reseller (Change 1 to the actual Reseller ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/reseller/1/status?status=approved
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------
### Reseller Login
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("resellerToken", response.body.token);
%}

### ----------------------------------------
### Admin Adds a Product (Use form-data in Postman due to File Upload)
### GET Products
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------
### Reseller Views Catalog
GET http://localhost:8080/reseller/catalog
Authorization: Bearer {{resellerToken}}

### ----------------------------------------
### Reseller Adds Product to Shop (Change Product ID 1)
POST http://localhost:8080/reseller/catalog
Authorization: Bearer {{resellerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "sellingPrice": 500
}

### ----------------------------------------
### Customer Views Shop
GET http://localhost:8080/shop/jane-shop

### ----------------------------------------
### Customer Checkout (Change productId to an existing one)
POST http://localhost:8080/shop/jane-shop/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "John Smith",
  "customerPhone": "0987654321",
  "customerAddress": "456 Sukhumvit",
  "productId": 1,
  "amountProduct": 2
}

### ----------------------------------------
### Customer Simulates Payment (replace 1 with the orderId created above)
POST http://localhost:8080/shop/jane-shop/payment/1

### ----------------------------------------
### Customer Tracks Order (Replace ORD-xxxxxx)
GET http://localhost:8080/track-order?orderNumber=ORD-123456789

### ----------------------------------------
### Admin Views All Orders
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------
### Admin Marks Order as Shipped (Find correct Order ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/orders/status?status=shipped
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "orderId": 1
}

### ----------------------------------------
### Reseller Views Wallet
GET http://localhost:8080/reseller/wallet
Authorization: Bearer {{resellerToken}}

### ----------------------------------------
### Admin Views Dashboard
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
